  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8f/8f8dc1ac864720cd77412a7a30a784ca.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Photo by Elon Schoenholz, courtesy of the Norton Simon Art Foundation\" data-size=\"2200x1467\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8f/8f8dc1ac864720cd77412a7a30a784ca.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8f/8f8dc1ac864720cd77412a7a30a784ca.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8f/8f8dc1ac864720cd77412a7a30a784ca.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/8f/8f8dc1ac864720cd77412a7a30a784ca.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Photo by Elon Schoenholz, courtesy of the Norton Simon Art Foundation\" alt=\"Photo by Elon Schoenholz, courtesy of the Norton Simon Art Foundation\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePhoto by Elon Schoenholz, courtesy of the Norton Simon Art Foundation\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003ePasadena’s Norton Simon Museum has previewed its upcoming $14 million Exterior Improvement Project from the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/_ARG\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eArchitectural Resources Group\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/swagroup\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSWA\u003c/a\u003e. Timed to coincide with the Museum’s 50th anniversary, the project entails facade conservation/enhancements and other improvements to outdoor areas along Colorado Boulevard. Accessibility will be improved through a \u0026#34;re-envisioned\u0026#34; entrance. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHeath Ceramics has been brought in to re-create its ceramic tiles where the originals are too damaged for repair, while, finally, new signage is being added courtesy of Hunt Design. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe museum expects work to be completed by the end of this fall.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/b3/b3f9233d6c97138e6207fe762939ed1d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/b3/b3f9233d6c97138e6207fe762939ed1d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/b3/b3f9233d6c97138e6207fe762939ed1d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/b3/b3f9233d6c97138e6207fe762939ed1d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/b3/b3f9233d6c97138e6207fe762939ed1d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eRendering of the Norton Simon Museum’s pedestrian walkway and main entrance, courtesy of ARG and SWA\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/73/73d7e4a2faa1df94d331a4250bbcba63.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x670\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https: